mple.</p></div><div class="clear rma"><div class="box right breakout"> <header><h2>Did You Know?</h2> </header><div><p>Household brands like BT, Sky and Virgin Media aren't the <em>only</em> companies racing to upgrade UK broadband speeds to next-generation full-fibre connections.&nbsp;It's worth keeping an eye on a number of (much) smaller broadband companies specialising in full-fibre internet, like&nbsp;<a data-link-tracking="InArticle|BreakoutTextBox"  href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=76202X1587086&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=Express---ExpressTech-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyperoptic.com%2Fprice-plans%2F" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate NetworkEvent', 'Skimlinks')"><strong>Hyperoptic</strong></a>,&nbsp;<strong><a data-link-tracking="InArticle|BreakoutTextBox"  href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=76202X1587086&amp;xs=1&amp;xcust=Express---ExpressTech-&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcommunityfibre.co.uk%2Fdeals" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate NetworkEvent', 'Skimlinks')">Community Fibre</a></strong>,&nbsp;<a data-link-tracking="InArticle|BreakoutTextBox"  href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=76202X1587086&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fzzoomm.com%2F&amp;xcust=ExpressTech" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate NetworkEvent', 'Skimlinks')"><strong>Zzoomm</strong></a>,&nbsp;<a data-link-tracking="InArticle|BreakoutTextBox"  href="https://go.skimresources.com/?id=76202X1587086&amp;xs=1&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.giganet.uk%2F&amp;xcust=ExpressTech" target="_blank" rel="nofollow" onclick="ExpressApp.GoogleAnalytics.TrackEvent('Affiliate NetworkEvent', 'Skimlinks')"><strong>Giganet</strong></a>. These firms offer 1Gbps download speeds ...or higher.</p><p>Lesser-known brands can offer incredible discounts that BT, Virgin Media and TalkTalk&nbsp;<em>never</em>&nbsp;come close to matching. So, <em>what's the catch?</